      "versionNonce": 1367907529,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1749536552353,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Why don't they have enough 2T?\n - Maybe filtered down < 4 by alt offers when de-duping\n - Model just didn't produce them\n - filter_offer_ids_availability_by_public_offer?\n - all country specific necessity",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Why don't they have enough 2T?\n - Maybe filtered down < 4 by alt offers when de-duping\n - Model just didn't produce them\n - filter_offer_ids_availability_by_public_offer?\n - all country specific necessity",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "z2mzFn68TJ7YqUwiBUgho",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4861.743032582092,
      "y": 662.2579988564044,
      "width": 630.1957397460938,
      "height": 70,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0P",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 564610244,
      "version": 720,
      "versionNonce": 1584607303,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1749536552353,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Why don't they have enough Personalised/Alt?\n - dedup order is alt, 2T, personalised so ",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Why don't they have enough Personalised/Alt?\n - dedup order is alt, 2T, personalised so ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qYl9ITZN2H5nkCCBEOON8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4864.49752259581,
      "y": 1921.3748634691085,
      "width": 1026.0133080101662,
      "height": 490,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#343a40",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "-Ij6MuKM5AKSK_49QdgCc",
        "2S3VBY6tUpSAcCj35wMS2"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0f",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1209880900,
      "version": 1486,
      "versionNonce": 1506548649,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1749536552353,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Breakdown: \n- only 659 (43%) have ANY recs\n-  removing region filter only boosts to 664 (+5 users)\n- only 451 (29.5%) have enough (4+ offers)\n\n\nso currently 1078/1528 users (70.5%) of the 1528 cohort of missing 2T\nemails \ndon't have enough 2T offers recommended by the model to qualify\n    \n    - could be due to\n        - lookback window differences\n        - cohort selection differences\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Breakdown: \n- only 659 (43%) have ANY recs\n-  removing region filter only boosts to 664 (+5 users)\n- only 451 (29.5%) have enough (4+ offers)\n\n\nso currently 1078/1528 users (70.5%) of the 1528 cohort of missing 2T emails \ndon't have enough 2T offers recommended by the model to qualify\n    \n    - could be due to\n        - lookback window differences\n        - cohort selection differences\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
